high_descs: Turn left and go through the large room, then right to the small platform with the microwave on it.
Pick up the knife that is inside the microwave.
Turn around and go to the sofa opposite the microwave.
Slice the tomato on the sofa.
Look down at the bowl on the sofa.
Place the knife next to the bowl.
Look back towards the tomato you just sliced.
Pick up one slice of the tomato.
Turn left and go straight ahead to the fridge in the corner of the room.
Place the tomato slice in the fridge, let it cool, then pick it back up.
Go back to the microwave you got the knife from.
Place the tomato slice inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled tomato slice inside a microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight  and turn your right to reach the microwave oven
Open the oven and take a knife from the oven and close it
Turn back and walk towards a couch
Cut a tomato into pieces
Little bit move towards left side of the couch
Put the knife on the couch
Little bit move towards right side of the couch
Take a piece of tomato from the cut tomato
Turn right and walk straight and turn towards cupboard
Open the door and put the tomato slice inside it and close the door. After few seconds, open the door and take out the tomato piece and close the door
Turn right and walk straight and turn towards your right to reach the oven
Open the oven and put the tomato slice into it and close the oven
anns.task_desc: Put the tomato slice in the oven

high_descs: Turn left go to the black microwave.
Pick up the knife from the microwave.
Turn around to the sofa.
Slice the tomato on the sofa.
Turn left and go to the middle of the sofa.
Place the knife on the sofa to the left of the bowl.
Turn right and go back to the tomato on the sofa.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the middle.
Turn left and go across to the fridge.
Place the tomato in the fridge beside the knife then pick it up.
Head back to the sofa and go across to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool slice of tomato in the microwave.
